---
title: Quick Chicken Strips & Warm Potato Salad with Cucumber & Parmesan Slaw
description: Eat the rainbow with this tasty mix of classic chicken shop flavours. Tender chicken strips get a lightly spiced coating, with a
warm, creamy potato salad and a crunchy cucumber slaw to round out the meal.
